Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你认为我太疯狂也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能否答应我 陪我实现这桩事业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我的疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让我成为创造新人类的神？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是神！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.82,0:00:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要成为 为人类照亮未来的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是EXA-DB孕育了它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就是人类历史错误的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要击败它 继承伊泽尔坎特大人的意志！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTA-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里附近就有EXA-DB…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能驾驭它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Legilis！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德… 原来是真实存在的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EXA-DB的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有自我防御技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那种无人机动战士的代号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用EXA-DB的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像生物一样不断进化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所谓怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它拥有的力量 无人可以想像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人请回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机动战士太危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是高达Legilis 您只身一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 它必须由我击败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我命中注定的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能在这里取胜 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就没有继承伊泽尔坎特大人意志的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承伊泽尔坎特大人的…意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧 什么是高达真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须做到和伊泽尔坎特大人那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者更高一层的觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则无法发挥这台高达的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这台高达Legilis
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将胜利掌握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敌系统报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监测到机动战士反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是资源开发小行星聚集的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没有情报显示周围有友军出战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 为防万一确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的第一要务是前往诺德拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行攻略拉·格拉密斯要塞的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没空沿途沾花惹草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续监视 有情况汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代号希德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13年前 让你身负重伤的怪物又露面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不清楚敌人的相貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这家伙袭击的舰船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是B班 请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来 这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 明明只是调查一艘漂流船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友军机？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰弗里 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德出现 证明EXA-DB就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会在这个节骨眼上遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要亲手摧毁EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必通知天神号吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不只是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是清剿威胁地球的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人必须一个不留全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲为了复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会将EXA-DB用于这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那样和维甘没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会使军事力量的平衡遭到破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让如今的联邦得到EXA-DB太过危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们暗中销毁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会找罪受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对它的能耐 我有切身体会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不会搞砸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴洛诺克 改变轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？我可没收到他们的联络…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打算去发生战斗的宇域吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的我行我素不是第一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 把适配器递给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人叫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这儿有点事 你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要和我们一起参加战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会追上你们的 别这副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任老人家自己去 不知会干出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没这能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷根本不听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的想法不可能轻易被改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真诚的交流绝不会白费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急着放弃 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷他一定明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变轨完成 锁定目标坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴洛诺克 全速航行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找那只怪物算账
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都给我打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到接近它会如此困难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甄选出值得生存下去的种群
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让人活得更有尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸计划将为我们打开通往新世界的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以把它理解成创造新的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知自己的所作所为 会造成怎样的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意听好 地球种们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘在此 宣布开始全面侵略地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特大人全心为人类的未来着想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否愿意陪我的疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓将人类 带往伊甸！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正逐渐发挥出Legilis的全部性能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种距离下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下方？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐身斗篷？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士竟然也有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原本就是来自EXA-DB的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德在成长过程中拥有 也不足为奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这块不算广阔的宇域里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EXA-DB可以隐匿至今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来和那种能力有密切关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在出去也只会碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fon·Farsia的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少可以成为杰哈特大人的盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你了解杰哈特大人的为人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能允许你这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗宇域附近发现反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机动战士！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错 是希德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去找出EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在火星上遇到过的维甘高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来碍事 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我自己的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是在考验我作为伊泽尔坎特大人继承者的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝你别来插手 尽快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特的继承者？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特 你这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和这东西有交战经验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少还记得它的行动规律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来吸引它 快逃 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在说这种话！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全无影无踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船…船长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的行动…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 那颗小行星里藏着EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样永远无法捉住它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如一试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锚索发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 看你往哪儿跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就在缆绳的末端
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中攻击那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缆绳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掌握了！高达Legilis的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于成功驾驭了高达Legilis
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 被诅咒的秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是EXA-DB吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你摧毁它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我让开 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 EXA-DB不能留在世上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EXA-DB对我军来说是必不可少的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看见它造出怎样的怪物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 EXA-DB的力量是被诅咒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有能力控制那样的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了人类的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中目标
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在确认EXA-DB是否完全被摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是你说要打的 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EXA-DB…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去它或许令人惋惜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我得到了高达Legilis的全部能力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特大人的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经继承了它
